{"tid":786612,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[狂賀]舐共狗759主席升仙之時, 股價爆升7成","createTime":"2018-08-20T05:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T17:03:45.000Z","uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa3810d0098e05a597312f7d7241d098efc3afbf","tid":786612,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"CEC國際 (<a href=\"http://00759.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00759.HK&d=U9OnEOAJg4rLPpZvfU9Q6PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4ef6fb35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00759.HK</a>) 公布創辦人兼主席和董事總經理林偉駿於上周末(18日)於養和醫院逝世，公司已於昨天(19日)起正式委任現集團執行董事鄧鳳群席接替林氏所有職務。聲明指、公司將盡力按已故主席訂立策略繼續經營集團業務及重組其架構。 市場憧憬CEC未來潛在重組可能，今早股價由六年低位大裂口高開27%，一舉重越五條平均線(250天線為0.58)，報0.59元遇壓，曾掉頭回順至0.53元拒絕再下，再度抽升兼突破52周高位0.75元，最高見0.91元，創逾14個月高，現造0.81元，勁彈74%，一向薄弱成交激增至2,950萬股，為逾四年罕見，涉資2,086萬元。(sz/t)~ 阿思達克財經新聞 網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=U9OnEOAJg4rLPpZvfU9Q6PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b47c89b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018-08-20 10:18:33"},{"pid":"435b9a8b6850fee846a56ed2d9731ef7f8f0cd89","tid":786612,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0419468c89e6f697faca3065a25e5ec078142d","tid":786612,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"疑似民建聯會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed73e06cb5ca3e4ab4d3a2b0422018a1e0171578","tid":786612,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1a0419468c89e6f697faca3065a25e5ec078142d","tid":786612,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"疑似民建聯會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyT